{
  "stem": "18520.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, the two guys going around in those wooden shoes with a stick-- a wooden stick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's over there-- [SPEAKING GERMAN] you know, you're dirty, you're filthy, and this and that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't want to wash.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN], ice cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't go in there-- ice cold, ice!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, so this is what we went through, and then they put us in-- in a-- in a barrack, filled up the barrack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet, naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now you go into the barrack, and a guy comes, you know, and the-- those barracks in Auschwitz used to be a Polish army camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five or six, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I think one or two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who-- who was remembering a number?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so this was-- they used to keep horses in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had the place where they used to eat the horses-- in both sides, horses, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this place-- they used to fill it up with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what they did now, they put a piece of wood on top, and they closed it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on both sides, people were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sitting this close-- each other close-- all the way till this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many people they packed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sitting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then comes in a guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He goes on top of this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're sticking their hands, you know, to put it up here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he holds it, and he said, who wants to live?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who wants to live?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You better give me the gold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Give me the-- the diamonds, what you hide it, you swallow it, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You give it because you're gonna be fried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You give the gold if you have it, and tell me where it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some people did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Did you have gold?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
